{"tid":53413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超強颱風洛坦聖誕橫掃菲律賓，預測近距離掠過馬尼拉一帶","createTime":"2016-12-24T16:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T11:47:05.000Z","uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64b54340b9e2092fe6c0228d5cbbe9d9b93e4bc2","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"超強颱風洛坦逐漸靠近菲律賓，預測將正面吹襲當地，沿岸數以千計居民要疏散。 在呂宋島南部的索索貢省受颱風影響，岸邊翻起大浪，大樹搖晃。當局撤離沿岸村落的居民。而在首都馬尼拉風勢亦明顯增強。<br />\n<br />\n 雖然地方政府暫時未發出警報，但有漁民已表示會暫停出海。氣象部門預計，洛坦將橫掃呂宋島，馬尼拉等地區，聖誕節期間有強風和大雨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/crifuav1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcrifuav1&h=6ad59071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dkyt5ai4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdkyt5ai4&h=9b6edeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賓國這個聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cb610e83a09303eef97224192442f09ec4d8cc","tid":53413,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"超強颱風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5361e43f7d8255e33457182c94f8e245072b1e9c","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lweoain1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flweoain1&h=c92da13f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77dc2736d1b61a391587ac83b571e26d3414a658","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xrsv0k1q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxrsv0k1q&h=64388fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fa74115a93861cec84b8fdc074b655c6cd7b41c","tid":53413,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"聖誕都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48458a2400cb9af0d60d5d3d5e0dc6c7a11a4eea","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖誕都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱帶無明顯四季，咁當然有颱風唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e285b53423260c5b9a6c5cc3d1c29875a70c7b3e","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"超強颱風洛坦迫近菲律賓中部，預料會帶來狂風大雨，當局擔心引發洪水及山泥傾瀉，阿爾拜省強制疏散二十萬戶家庭，合共超過一百萬人。<br />\n<br />\n陣風時速達到二百一十五公里的洛坦，凌晨距離首都馬尼拉以東六百多公里，以時速十四公里移向菲律賓中部，預料今日下午至傍晚登陸卡坦端內斯省，沿岸可能出現超過兩米高的大浪。氣象人員說，洛坦的風力會在登陸後減弱，但移向南部呂宋及馬尼拉時會再度增強。"},{"pid":"e500d0c29db636519707386537824d6480b23cee","tid":53413,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q2ckz16r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq2ckz16r&h=274aa210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n登錄一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}